data.description: A beautiful centerally located corner home with lots of upgrades and updating. Recent upgrades (2023) include a new roof, exterior painting, all new kitchen appliances, pavers and landscaping, insulated garage door and the main bathroom. In 2020, the seller added a tankless hot water system and installed a new HVAC system. Home includes a softwater system, plantation shutters and driveway gate. The drive gate opens to secure area. Backyard is set up for a large and secure play area or additional parking. Minutes to 51, Biltmore area, resturants and shopping.
